<h2 class="heading-2 hire-me__heading">You can hire me, if you want</h2>
<div class="hire-me__main">
  <p class="text--lede margin--bottom-2">I'm looking to join a fantastic team. I
  just moved back from San Francisco, with 8+ years of experience I'd like to share.</p>
  <p>My name is <a href="/about" class="link">Jake Holman</a>, and I'm available to
  start working for you right away. Here's a bit about what I'm looking for, and what I'm not:</p>
  <p class="text--center margin--top-3 margin--bottom-1"><a href="/media/Jake%20Holman%2C%20Product%20Manager%20%26%20Leader%20-%20CV.pdf"
     target="_blank" class="button button--full">Download My CV/Resume (PDF)</a></p>
